Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:08.40,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kimi ni kono koe ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:11.24,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,todokimasu youni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:19.29,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,karamitsuku kaze o surinuke ima negau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.96,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,ashita o sekasu kodou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:29.63,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku wa itsu kara ka tomadoi kakushiteta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:35.18,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,samenai yume ni mayotte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:41.19,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kuri kaesu hibi ni ibasho o sagashiteta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:47.19,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kimi ni deai muryoku o shiri
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:53.45,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kakae kirenai hikari ni mo fureta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:59.75,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,soko ni nani ga atte imi naku aretatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:04.88,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kotae awase ja tsumaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:11.13,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,kimi ni kono koe ga todokimasu youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:19.56,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yaketsuku toki o surinuke ima negau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:08.40,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,So that my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:11.24,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,is able to reach you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:19.29,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I hope to survive this entangling wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.96,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I will be completely without direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:29.63,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,in the fast paced world of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:35.18,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,When I was lost in my own dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:41.19,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I was looking for a place to belong in this modern age.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:47.19,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,When I met you, I learned what true strength is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:53.45,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Now that I've touched what could barely be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:59.75,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Without any other knowledge, without having a solid reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:04.88,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I've found my answer that a skeptic would just ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:11.13,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,So that my voice is able to reach you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:19.56,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I hope to survive this scorching era.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Intro}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,'I'll be back!'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've returned! Gaaash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Patie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We just fought not too long ago\Nand you're already here for payback?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, payback? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to burn your book\Nfor sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come forth, the warriors\Nfrom a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:24.54,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs55\pos(488,500)}Patie's Revenge!!\NThe Release of the Assassins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Warriors from a thousand years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To eliminate all the remaining demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your book...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to be burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, my servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth and destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are these strange\Nenemies so eager for battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Three enemies at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They've caught up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! He's casting a spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash! Kick the demon's right leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Hit him as hard as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we have to find a\Nplace without any people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So dramatic! So dramatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight's just started\Nand you're already out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Patie, if they're from\N1,000 years ago, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they in the previous fight to\Ndecide the ruler of the demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One thousand years later,\Nin the human world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have to do with\Ntheir rage and hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll answer your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But, these demons won't\Nstop fighting for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you survive long enough\Nto hear the whole answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Guransen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Biraitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashirudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, we deflected them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they'll attack them instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bireiorudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he deflected them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Aren't they strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got thousand years of malice\Npent up inside them from being stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These demons met something named the\NStone Golem in the battle 1,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He transformed them and their\Nbooks into living stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor dears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to return to the Demon World,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they were forced to remain as\Nstone tablets, about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stone tablets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The stone tablets Dad and I found?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you know of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They owe it all to Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She freed them from\Ntheir everlasting hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you two have been chosen\Nto receive their anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Guranga Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring forth the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The strong power of our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong enough to deflect this spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, he's in range!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Using only the minimum spell\Nneeded to subdue the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It shows your level of\Nexperience in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't conserve your spells, you run\Nout of life energy to continue the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, when fighting enemies\Nfrom 1,000 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bodies are much stronger than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply adore those faces!\NThose looks of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you feel how your chances\Nof winning have crumbled?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's worse is that they still\Nhaven't used their strongest spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Gash-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you to a pulp\Nand make you disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! That was a direct hit!\NHe should have fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganzu Biraitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash. Carry me on your\Nshoulders and run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go catch them and finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. They've all lined up\Ntogether and followed us in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Gash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This will decide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Against these three enemies,\Nthis is our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this and prepare to be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Baou Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Daibara Biranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigano Garanzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NTwo of them at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No! The Baou Zakeruga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like even your strongest\Nspell wasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it took all your strength to hide\Nyour book under your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're going to keep\Nfighting without any spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What touching courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't be lenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Patie, I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do the thousand-year-old demons\Nhave humans able to use their books?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You stumbled onto an interesting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, no human could\Nlive for a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They used their own comrade as a shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How despicable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash-kun. You're risking your life by letting\Nsuch a foolish feeling get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. They are just underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a conscience or feelings,\Nthey are just tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When they see Baou Zakeruga,\Nalmost anyone would balk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But their partners, far from being scared,\Nmanaged to counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like their demons, they\Nshow no hesitation in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, they don't have a\Nsingle thought beyond the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No thought outside the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're being controlled by Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really is Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why Lord respects you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But why can they use the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In some distant ruins, Lord\Nfound the stone tablets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She revived the demons and their books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they told Lord the names of their\Npartners from 1,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving the books to her servant Byonko,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,she sent him to their homelands\Nto search for their descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And she gathered everyone\Nwhom the books reacted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the fact they were descendants\Nwouldn't mean they could use the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So she experimented\Non them, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But almost none of them\Ncould even read the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one of them was able\Nto actually cast a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So the human's heart and the books\Nmust be perfectly me... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Meshing gears?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The gears didn't mesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how is it that\Nthose gears mesh now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With Lord's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With her ability to control minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,she forced the humans to match\Nthe difference in the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if their minds match,\Nnow the wa... wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wavelengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Now the wavelengths\Nmatched perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And taking advantage of this, she made\Nthem concentrate only on the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there are humans\Nwho dislike fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And cowardly people, and\Ntender-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kinds of people have to be made\Ninto fighting machines to be of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we erased everything\Nexcept their will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong enough to easily\Nbring you to your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... have any idea\Nwhat you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even move, and you\Nstill want to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Manipulating the hearts of those who don't\Nwant to fight and forcing them to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him live!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Koruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Koruru... I'm Shiori, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NYou're turning back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Koruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My sweet Koruru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Gash-kun,\Nfor stopping Koruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Gash?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis Shiori! You're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I did all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My other side got out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone got hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She was crying tears of pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're doing things\Neven worse than her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even move to cast your spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend you can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Controlling people's minds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Forcing peaceful people to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never forgive that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can never let anyone\Nlike that become the ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't lose to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I never...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,want to see those tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousand-year-old warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're at your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your last attack didn't\Nhave a bit of power in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard you cry,\Nyou can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are close to 40 of the\Nthousand-year-old demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They fight better!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Two meager bugs talking big\Ncan never match them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Guransen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganzu Biraitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them become ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seushiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gash! Kiyomaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You two aren't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got strong allies too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:12.63,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Stars atarashii mirai e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.51,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,akiramenai hitori janai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.89,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,mou mayowanai yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.90,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me no mae no genjitsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,he kon de shimau koto hoshi no kazu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:44.78,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuugure no aka wo mita
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.79,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku ni hitsuyou na kawaranai yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:53.71,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,boku wa boku de kimi wa kimi no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.88,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,yuzurenai jounetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:04.59,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,me wo sorasazu ni tatakai tsuzukeru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.73,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,sorezore no nido to nai toki wo kizamou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.82,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,shinjitsu wa Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.62,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,toki no nagare ni makenaide arukou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:30.83,Karaoke,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:12.63,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,Stars, to the new tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:17.51,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't give up, you are not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:23.89,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I have no more doubts, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.90,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the truth before my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.90,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,to the things I give in to, the number of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:44.78,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,I saw the redness of evening
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.79,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,the unchanging courage that I need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:53.71,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,me and mine, you and yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:57.88,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,unyielding passion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:04.59,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't turn your eyes away, continue to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.22,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,We've gotta take the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:14.73,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,try to carve the moments that won't come again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:18.82,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,truth is Rhythm Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.62,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,don't lose to the flow of time, walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:30.83,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show them our combination, Gash!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that girl?! Why's she\Nso friendly to Gash-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tio! Megumi-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All you weaklings will\Nbe crushed together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight isn't about numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll see our new spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Konjiki no Gash Bell:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light of Hope, Saifojio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:22:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Kiyomaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in us, your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs60\bord3\pos(488,435)}The Light of Hope, Saifojio

